Pico 3 active firmware: painting rotation puzzle.

This folder name is historical. It no longer drives the TV wall trigger.
Archived TV wall code is in:

../../pico-back-room-blender-final/unused-future-puzzles/

Hardware:
- GPIO 15: RC35 magnetic sensor, reed switch, or equivalent hall-style sensor

Main topics:
- Publishes escape/pico3/painting_rotation_complete
- Subscribes escape/cmd/pico3/enable_painting_rotation
- Subscribes escape/cmd/all/status_request
- Subscribes escape/cmd/all/reset_puzzle

The Raspberry Pi plays assets/crashing_plates.m4a when this puzzle completes.
